<header>
  <h1>Privacy Policy — SF PermLens (Permission Manager for Salesforce)</h1>
  <div class="meta">
    <div><strong>Last updated:</strong> 27 June 2026</div>
    <div><strong>Developer / Publisher:</strong> Vasanth</div>
